      <title>福特首席执行官认为 3 级自动驾驶将为驾驶员节省时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/ford-ceo-sees-level-3-autonomy-giving-time-back-to-drivers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[福特首席执行官吉姆·法利表示，福特距离推出 3 级自动驾驶仅剩几年的时间，届时驾驶员将不再需要专心驾驶。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-03/ford-ceo-sees-level-3-autonomy-giving-time-back-to-drivers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 10:38:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
