    <item>
      <title>民意调查预测莫迪获胜，印度股市创下新高，卢比上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/india-s-stock-futures-rally-as-polls-predict-landslide-modi-win</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在出口民意调查显示总理纳伦德拉·莫迪领导的执政党取得压倒性胜利后，印度股市飙升至历史最高水平，而卢比和主权债券价格也出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/india-s-stock-futures-rally-as-polls-predict-landslide-modi-win</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 01:05:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：降息预期坚定，亚洲股市早盘上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-as-rate-cut-bets-firm-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于新的人工智能芯片推动了 Nvidia Corp. 和 Advanced Micro Devices Inc. 的上涨，大型科技股在经历了三天的低迷之后有望上涨。GameStop Corp. 的股价在模因股热潮的回归中翻了一番。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-02/asian-stocks-eye-early-gains-as-rate-cut-bets-firm-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Jun 2024 22:36:17 GMT</pubDate>
